job_detail:
@每日公司產品進貨管理、理貨整理、出貨包裝、退貨整理等工作事宜。
@每日公司商品庫存整理與檢查。
@環境清潔整理。
@其他主管交辦事項。

工作內容:
1. 協同各單位，根據工程案件用品的需求量、預測量或商品庫存量，執行訂購作業。
2. 負責供應商開發工作。
3. 制定年度採購計畫、評析市場原物料或設備供應資訊。
4. 定期進行請款作業，並整理相關表單（如：請款單、驗收單、訂購單）。
5. 建立、更新供應商資料（如：貨品價格比較、規格和到貨時間），以選擇最佳供應商。
6.供應商關係維護
7.電腦文書檔案管理工作。

希望你:
@喜歡團體協作共事
@對數字、金額敏感
@喜歡和人聊天
@喜歡採購工作、並樂於議價
@會因為殺價成功又讓老闆開心，或是買到便宜好物而感到心跳加速熱血沸騰


@熟悉視聽、門禁、中央監控、弱電相關等電子電力設備產品為佳，優先安排面試。

other:
1.Master or higher in Mechanical Engineering or relevant engineering disciplines;
2.Proficient in Creo, Solidwork or equivalent 3-D CAD software with good command of GD&T skills
3.Prior experience in fiber-optic transceiver product design in accordance with standard multisource agreements (MSA) for optical transceivers.
4.Hands-on experience in thermal and structural simulation using ANSYS or other FEA tools;
5.Experience of precision manufacturing processes and tooling construction of machining, stamping, die casting, and injection moulding is a plus;
6.Excellent interpersonal and communication skills for direct interaction with customers and vendors; 
7.Ability to communicate effectively in a multilingual environment (English and Mandarin)
8.Ability to handle multiple tasks, independent, self-motivated, creative, innovative and responsible.

job_detail:
Job Summary：
Develop fastener and precision components business in Taiwan.

Job Responsibilities:
1. Develop and implement middle term plan;
2. Maintain existing key accounts and expand customer base;
3. Establish and maintain excellent relationship with major tiers and OEMs;
4. Manage RFQs, determine price and contractual conditions;
5. Negotiate & conclude supply contracts and price;
6. Observe market and competition;
7. Support Customer Service team regarding delivery and inventory issues;
8. Cooperate with quality department in dealing with customer concerns;
9. Insure internal and external flow of information.

Job Requirements：
1. Bachelor’s degree or above, mechanical engineering preferred;
2. 5-10 years in Taiwan ODM/OEM/EMS for hardware components dealing with mechanical design Engineer and buyer from ODM/OEM/EMS.;
3. Eager to achieve goals, target oriented management style;
4. Sales Experience from Foxconn, Compal, Inventec, Wistron, Delta, metal chassis of server and PC;
5. Good personality and communication skills to talk to people on all hierarchy levels;
6. Willingness to travel intensively.

